s Forum\" href=\"/support/forum/presale-questions/\">presale questions</a>, <a title=\"Feature Request Forum\" href=\"/support/forum/feature-requests/\">feature requests</a> and <a title=\"Bug Report Forum\" href=\"/support/forum/bug-reports/\">bug reports</a>. There are even private support forums for customers who have purchased a premium template or add-on plugin. These private forums are limited to only those who have purchased a premium template or add-on plugin. They receive priority support over the general support forums, bringing even more value to your purchases!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/2013/01/04/support-forums/\">Support Forums</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com\">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~4/LJhiQuHS2Xs\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://connections-pro.com/2013/01/04/support-forums/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"28\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"http://connections-pro.com/2013/01/04/support-forums/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Eshop / Cart Upgrade\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~3/I-RYKsc1TFI/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 27 Dec 2012 20:53:18 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Announcement\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Connections\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"http://connections-pro.com/?p=248247\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:570:\"<p>Back in September the eshop / cart was upgraded to bring you easier access to your past purchases and free updates via your &#8220;Purchase History&#8220;. Since September the old and new eshop/carts were running so access could still could be provided to everyone who had purchased items before September. If you purchased items before September, ...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/\">Eshop / Cart Upgrade</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com\">Connections</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Steven Zahm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1686:\"<p>Back in September the eshop / cart was upgraded to bring you easier access to your past purchases and free updates via your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. Since September the old and new eshop/carts were running so access could still could be provided to everyone who had purchased items before September.</p>\n<p>If you purchased items before September, over the past two days, your account has been migrated to the new eshop/cart. This migration triggered an email invoice for your past purchases which provides the details of your order, the download links and a link to your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;. <strong>There are <em>no</em> additional charges or fees associated with your account migration</strong>. The old eshop/cart has been discontinued and removed. The download link and code you received with your original order will no longer function as of today. Please access your purchases from your &#8220;<a title=\"My Account Purchase History\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/my-account/purchase-history/\">Purchase History</a>&#8220;.</p>\n<p>I thank you in advance for your understanding and patience. Happy New Years to you and yours!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/\">Eshop / Cart Upgrade</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com\">Connections</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~4/I-RYKsc1TFI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/12/27/eshop-cart-upgrade/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"Feature Preview: Form — Email Notifications\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/connections-pro/news/~3/RPqrxOPlv9Q/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"http://connections-pro.com/2012/10/09/feature-preview-form-email-notifications/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s