:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:589:\"<p>Excerpt has received a significant update to take full advantage of all the newer features built into Connections which include: Responsive theme compatible. Over 40 shortcode options that can be used to customize the template to your needs. Easier installation. You now install Excerpt like you would any other plugin. If you are upgrading from an ...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/22/template-update-excerpt-2-0/\">Template Update: Excerpt 2.0</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://connections-pro.com\">Connections</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Steven Zahm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13632:\"<p>Excerpt has received a significant update to take full advantage of all the newer features built into Connections which include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\">Responsive theme compatible.</span></li>\n<li>Over <a href=\"http://connections-pro.com/documentation/slim/slim-shortcode-options/\">40 shortcode options</a> that can be used to customize the template to your needs.</li>\n<li>Easier installation. You now install Excerpt like you would any other plugin. If you are upgrading from an older version, make sure to delete it first.</li>\n<li>And lastly, the number one feature request, an easy way to change the color. Here&#8217;s a few examples:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Excerpt in its default blue:</p>\n<div id=\"cn-top\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;\"></div><div class=\"cn-list\" id=\"cn-list\" data-connections-version=\"8.1.5-0.1.9\"><div class=\"cn-template cn-excerpt\" id=\"cn-excerpt\" data-template-version=\"3.0.1\">\n<div class=\"cn-list-head cn-clear\" id=\"cn-list-head\">\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"connections-list cn-list-body cn-clear\" id=\"cn-list-body\">\n<div class=\"cn-list-section-head\" id=\"cn-char-D\"></div><div class=\"cn-list-row-alternate vcard individual demo show\" id=\"john-doe\" data-entry-type=\"individual\" data-entry-id=\"1\" data-entry-slug=\"john-doe\">\n<div id=\"entry-id-15480f4300ad9c\" class=\"cn-entry cn-accordion\">\n\n	<div class=\"cn-left\">\n<span class=\"cn-image-style\"><span style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; width: 100px\"><a href=\"http://connections-pro.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img height=\"120\" width=\"100\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"cn-image photo\" alt=\"Photo of John Doe\" title=\"Photo of John Doe\" srcset=\"http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/connections-images/john-doe/920640_38936495_SM_original-bc1dd15b948045102ed103bc00a9c0f9.jpg 1x\"/></a></span></span>\n</div><div class=\"cn-right\"><h3 class=\"cn-accordion-item\" id=\"cn-accordion-item-15480f4300ad9c\" data-uuid=\"15480f4300ad9c\" style=\"border-bottom: #00508D 1px solid; color:#00508D;\"><span class=\"cn-sprite\" id=\"cn-toggle-15480f4300ad9c\" style=\"background-color: #00508D;\"></span>\n<span class=\"fn n\"> <span class=\"given-name\">John</span> <span class=\"family-name\">Doe</span> </span>\n</h3><div class=\"cn-excerpt\" id=\"cn-excerpt-15480f4300ad9c\"><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc varius placerat hendrerit. Pellentesque porttitor pharetra felis et feugiat. Aliquam tempor luctus sodales. Quisque porttitor nunc eu nunc tempor non suscipit urna interdum. Nulla enim metus, vestibulum et sagittis a, egestas et mauris. Integer sit amet dolor ante, quis gravida est. Integer quis leo lectus. Vivamus diam tortor,&hellip;</p><span class=\"cn-show-more\" data